              Required**   Range**                       

  Iron        Proficient   4--6        Iron Sword        Shops, common
                                                         drops

  Steel       Proficient   7--9        Steel Lance       Shops (Act 2+),
                                                         uncommon drops

  Silver      Proficient   10--12      Silver Axe        Rare drops, elite
                                                         rewards

  Legendary   Mastery      13--16+     Ragnell, Falchion Boss drops,
                                                         special events.
                                                         Unique effects.
